02:28:21.769 --> 02:28:23.062
Mã đỏ.

02:28:23.729 --> 02:28:24.730
Nick.

02:28:26.398 --> 02:28:27.399
Hill.

02:28:42.331 --> 02:28:43.499
Ôi không.

02:28:45.125 --> 02:28:46.126
Trời đánh...

02:28:52.750 --> 02:29:04.000
ĐANG GỬI...
